results.name: Signature permutation of a Catalan automorphism: row 2 of A130402.
comment: The signature-permutation of the Catalan automorphism which is derived from *A069775 with recursion schema ENIPS (see A122204 for the definition).
link: A. Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2055
Index entries for signature-permutations of Catalan automorphisms
xref: Inverse: A130936. The number of cycles in range [A014137(n-1)..A014138(n-1)] of this permutation are given by A130969. The number of fixed points begins like A003238. Maximum cycle sizes begins like A000792 (shifted once right).
